name: "The Day I Married a Dead Poet"
description:
"When i arrived home from a meeting with a young teacher, i put my head on the pillow and started to dream. The "Dead Poet" we were mentioning at that meeting came to visit me, and i ended up marrying that "thing". I didn't really understand what was going on, and it was too late when i regained my consciousness. I was trapped in that agreement."
